    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1 class="display-4">Discover Tokyo: A City of Vibrant Culture and Rich History</h1>
        <p class="lead">Tokyo, the capital of Japan, is a city like no other. From its neon-lit streets to its ancient temples, Tokyo is a place where tradition meets innovation. With its unique blend of modern and traditional culture, Tokyo has something to offer for every kind of traveler.</p>
        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2>Shibuya Crossing</h2>
                <img src="https://image.pollinations.ai/prompt/Shibuya%20Crossing" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Shibuya Crossing">
                <p>One of the busiest intersections in the world, Shibuya Crossing is a must-see for any visitor to Tokyo. The area is known for its shopping, dining, and entertainment options, and is a great place to experience the city's vibrant energy.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2>Meiji Shrine</h2>
                <img src="https://image.pollinations.ai/prompt/Meiji%20Shrine" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Meiji Shrine">
                <p>Dedicated to the deified spirits of Emperor Meiji and his wife, Empress Shoken, the Meiji Shrine is a serene Shinto shrine located in a tranquil forested area. The shrine is a peaceful oasis in the midst of the bustling city, and is a great place to learn about Japanese culture and history.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2>Tokyo Tower</h2>
                <img src="https://image.pollinations.ai/prompt/Tokyo%20Tower" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Tokyo Tower">
                <p>At 332.9 meters tall, Tokyo Tower is one of the city's most iconic landmarks. The tower offers stunning views of the city from its observation decks, and is a great place to see the sunset or enjoy the city's nightlife.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-5">
            <img src="https://image.pollinations.ai/prompt/map%20of%20Tokyo%20style%20minimal" alt="Map of Tokyo" style="width:100%; border-radius:10px;">
        </div>
    </div>
